'''ResSystem''' was a [[Chemist/Legends|chemical]]-manufacturing company that existed during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial era]]. They created synthetic [[byrothsis]] which was used by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces in [[Heat Sensor Trip]]s.

